{"tid":1543892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【727 元朗】廂內放置藤條　私家車被毁　車尾箱藏棍刀大量武器","createTime":"2019-09-05T11:04:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T11:36:06.000Z","uid":168169,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ded8439ff1a04818b522e950aad13de1c34fd34e","tid":1543892,"uid":168169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:04:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/727-%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97-%E5%BB%82%E5%85%A7%E6%94%BE%E7%BD%AE%E8%97%A4%E6%A2%9D-%E7%A7%81%E5%AE%B6%E8%BB%8A%E8%A2%AB%E6%AF%81-%E8%BB%8A%E5%B0%BE%E7%AE%B1%E8%97%8F%E6%A3%8D%E5%88%80%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F727-%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597-%25E5%25BB%2582%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%2594%25BE%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E8%2597%25A4%25E6%25A2%259D-%25E7%25A7%2581%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25BB%258A%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25AF%2581-%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25B0%25BE%25E7%25AE%25B1%25E8%2597%258F%25E6%25A3%258D%25E5%2588%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2587%258F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%2599%25A8%2F&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MEVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=6a1017da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F727-%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597-%25E5%25BB%2582%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%2594%25BE%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E8%2597%25A4%25E6%25A2%259D-%25E7%25A7%2581%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25BB%258A%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25AF%2581-%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25B0%25BE%25E7%25AE%25B1%25E8%2597%258F%25E6%25A3%258D%25E5%2588%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2587%258F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%2599%25A8%2F&h=328fa7c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/727-%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97-%E5%BB%82%E5%85%A7%E6%94%BE%E7%BD%AE%E8%97%A4%E6%A2%9D-%E7%A7%81%E5%AE%B6%E8%BB%8A%E8%A2%AB%E6%AF%81-%E8%BB%8A%E5%B0%BE%E7%AE%B1%E8%97%8F%E6%A3%8D%E5%88%80%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大批市民今日到「元朗一日遊」，警方下午 5 時起清場，爆發衝突。傍晚在元朗西鐵站下，近南邊圍村對出的公眾停車場咪錶位位置，有人發現該處的一輛私家車，車內有藤條及一頂有軍徽的疑似內地人員帽。車輛其後被示威者嚴重損毁，車窗被扑爛。<br />\n<br />\n有示威者之後撬開車尾箱，發現內藏日本刀、鐵通、木棍等武器。除了武器外，車尾箱內有數簿和信件，上面寫有非華裔裔人士的名和南邊圍地址。<br />\n<br />\n《香港 01》查冊後發現，車主名為 Karunanayaka Mudiyanselage, Eranda M.，他的註冊地址位於元朗八鄉錦莆路吳家村，該名男子持有本地身份證。"},{"pid":"7d0c76fb03d7091b4a04f1cf7835be3c6f317fad","tid":1543892,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:04:42.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 出咗不反對啦！【9月6 反濫捕 抗威權 遮打集會】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1543083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1543083</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KTsuWvi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKTsuWvi.jpg&h=59781468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ud9tv0z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUd9tv0z.jpg&h=17d13451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wcJFfrO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwcJFfrO.jpg&h=7f9dd8d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TjeJddu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjeJddu.jpg&h=e690fd03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHcuNJL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHcuNJL.jpg&h=417a49e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07d0ffccb33c8f3d6f3d7b22237a2ae6707c49d3","tid":1543892,"uid":261385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:05:21.000Z","msg":"推，聽日記者會"},{"pid":"c44ae8fef04c198c06a22c1bc532c4cdaffda6e0","tid":1543892,"uid":168169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/27ADVit.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F27ADVit.jpg&h=c48b10de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e34f72b78504a5c5ac1bc621773285d4addc9c63","tid":1543892,"uid":168169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:09:52.000Z","msg":"推